A banner to display story details for Breaking News.

Usage:
```hbs
  <NyprMTextBanner
    @category='Breaking News'
    @url='Link'
    @route={{array 'article' 'slug'}}
    @title='Story Title'
    @description='Short summary of the story'
  />
```

